# Testing

- Add unit tests for pure mappers and domain helpers before relying on UI tests.
- Repository tests should mock external clients and assert data flow, not SDK internals.
- When changing turn, scoring, session, or persistence behavior, run focused tests for the touched domain/application/infrastructure areas.
- Keep fixtures small but representative: include teams, participants, board tiles, answered tiles, turn state, and mímica when testing session round-trips.
